                            <comment id="14047573" author="dominicletz" created="Mon, 30 Jun 2014 11:37:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching patch for the catch block to assign streamId&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14057665" author="thobbs" created="Thu, 10 Jul 2014 16:56:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The actual fix that&apos;s needed is to catch Throwables in Message.Dispatcher.messageReceived() (instead of just catching Exception) so that we cover QueryMessage and BatchMessage as well as ExecuteMessage.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The attached 7470.txt applies to 1.2.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
